9 An Act relating to public finance; enacting the
Strategic Bitcoin Reserve Act; providing definitions;
10 permitting certain investments by the State
Treasurer; limiting investments; directing manner in
11 which digital assets shall be held; permitting
certain third-party solution; permitting investment
12 of state retirement funds in certain digital assets;
providing for codification; and providing an
13 effective date.
